      "company": "amazon",
      "displayName": "Amazon",
      "year": 2011,
      "source": "careers",
      "text": "Work hard. Have fun. Make history. Build your future with Amazon! Amazon… a place where builders can build. We hire the world’s brightest minds and offer them an environment in which they can relentlessly improve the experience for our customers. We want you to help share and shape our mission to be Earth’s most customer-centric company. Amazon’s evolution from Web site to e-commerce partner to de",
